name: Cat Goes BRRRR
description:
I made this game in 24 hours for the 1-day jam!

You play as a bad cat and you eat salami which gives kills you but then you go into a spiritual dimension and gain psychic salami powers! Which you use to get to your owner's special box ;3

Controls- Arrow keys and mouse
